## Associations in Fixtures

### belongs_to

```yaml
# test/fixtures/articles.yml

one:
  user: john  # References users fixture
  title: First Article
  body: This is the first article body
  status: published
  published_at: <%= 1.day.ago %>

two:
  user: jane
  title: Second Article
  body: This is the second article body
  status: draft
```

### has_many :through

```yaml
# test/fixtures/tags.yml

ruby:
  name: Ruby

rails:
  name: Rails

javascript:
  name: JavaScript
```

```yaml
# test/fixtures/article_tags.yml

one:
  article: one
  tag: ruby

two:
  article: one
  tag: rails

three:
  article: two
  tag: javascript
```

